    <item>
      <title>派拉蒙裁减更多职位，作为裁员计划的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/paramount-cuts-more-jobs-as-part-of-planned-reductions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[派拉蒙全球公司周二进一步裁员，这是该公司先前宣布的将其美国员工人数减少 15%（约 2,000 个）计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/paramount-cuts-more-jobs-as-part-of-planned-reductions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 13:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管智能电视正在普及，Roku 仍“非常致力于”机顶盒业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/roku-remains-very-committed-to-set-top-boxes-even-as-smart-tvs-spread</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Roku Inc. 表示，即使电子行业转向内置流媒体技术的智能电视，该公司仍“非常致力于”其同名机顶盒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/roku-remains-very-committed-to-set-top-boxes-even-as-smart-tvs-spread</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
